# Safety Rules for PII Scrubber

- NEVER print the content of the CSV to the console/chat.
- ALWAYS use python scripting to process the data. Do NOT edit the CSV line-by-line manually.
- When generating the script:
    - Mask emails like `a***@example.com`.
    - Hash phones or use `***-***-****`.
    - Do NOT mask non-PII fields like `id` or `tier`.
